title: House Republicans hope to pass Israel aid package, setting up a clash with the Senate
description: Speaker Mike Johnson and House Republicans are hoping to pass aid $14.3 billion in aid to Israel as it fights Hamas coupled with cuts in IRS funding.

title: Will the Israeli-Hamas conflict spark a wider regional war, pulling in the U.S.?
description: The conflict between Israel and Hamas militants in Gaza has Western officials increasingly concerned that it could trigger a wider war that draws in more nations.
